ResourceHeader.ResourceName: MMS 1 Energetic Particle Detector, Energetic Ion Spectrometer (EPD-EIS) Electron Energy Spectra, Level 2, Burst Survey
ResourceHeader.Description: Energetic Particle Detector (EPD), Energetic Ion Spectrometer (EIS) Electron Energy Spectra, Level 2, Burst Survey, 0.605 s Data. The EIS provides ion composition measurements (protons versus oxygen ions) and angular distributions over the energy range from approximately 45 to 500 keV.
